 So far we, the world has detonated just under 500 mega-tons of nuclear bombs ABOVE GROUND. So i think that using a few more kilo-tons worth for space travel is justified. I think we need ships capable of diverting asteroids at a SAFE distance from earth. I also think we need a sustainable outpost off planet, either the moon , mars, or possibly orbital, incase of some super virus or unforseen natural problem arrises. Survival of the species is simply the most important goal ever. All other considerations are secondary.<br>
