<!--EZCODE QUOTE START--><blockquote><strong><em>Quote:</em></strong><hr>Any of the infinite &quot;ordinary&quot; failures would drop glass reactors sizzzling with gaseous fission products into the biosphere.<hr></blockquote><!--EZCODE QUOTE END--><br>
